E-01 CANCL OR CHG WAS APPOINTED, BUT PROC M/F DOESN'T EXIST
E-02 PROCESS M/F IS INPUT OVER 15 PROCESSES
E-03 PROCESS CODE IS INPUT, BUT SECTION CODE IS NOT INPUT
E-04 PROCESS CODE IS NOT INPUT & ONLY SECTION CODE IS INPUT
E-05 PROCESS CODE IS INPUT, BUT LOCATION IS NOT INPUT
E-06 PROCESS CODE IS NOT INPUT, BUT LOCATION IS INPUT
E-07 APPOINTED PROCESS NO IS TOO BIG
E-08 WHEN IT'S CHILD PART NBR, CAN'T CHG BEFORE REVERSE PRO
E-09 2 PROCESS CONTINUES CANNOT  CANCEL
E-10 THE PROC CD THERE WASN'T IN PROC NAME M/F HAD INPUT
E-11 ALL ITEM OF ADD PROCESS IS NOT INPUT
E-12 THERE ISN'T PROCESS CODE TO ADD IN PROCESS NAME M/F
E-13 KANBAN CHANGE DATE(FIRST 6 COLUMNS) IS LOGICAL ERROR
E-14 KANBAN CHANGE DATE BIN(LAST 2 COLUMNS) IS LOGICAL ERROR
E-15 PROCESS CODE INPUT REPEATEDLY,
E-16 RETUR NEXT PROC P/N BY KEY P/N COMBINATION                        R
E-17 IT ISN'T OVER 15 PROCE WITH INQ PROC NO OF CHILD P/N
E-18 APPOINT LAST TIME ERR CHG INST.(USUAL=. ,CHG=*)
E-19 THERE ISN'T THE SECTION WHICH WILL INPUT IN DETAILS M/F
E-20 KEY PART NUMBER CHANGE SCREEN   DO NOT ACCEPT CMD2
E-21 KEY PART NUMBER CHANGE SCREEN  DO NOT ACCEPT CMD3
E-22 THERE ISN'T PROC NO APPOINTED INQ PROC NO OF CHILD P/N
E-23 KEY PART NUMBER CHANGE SCREEN  DON'T ACCEPT CMD9
E-24 PROCESS IS NEVER INPUT
E-25 PROCESS IS INPUT, BUT CAN NOT PICK UP KEY PART NUMBER
E-26 THOUGH PROC ISN'T INPUT, PROC KEY PART NUMBER HAS INPUT
E-27 K CHG DATE & DATE BEFORE CHG ARE EQ OR 1ST ONE IS SMALL
E-28 LOCATION IN THE PROCESS WHICH CAN USE DOESN'T EXIST
E-29 DIFFERENT FROM KANBAN KIND OF INTRA-PROC LOC M/F
E-30 KANBAN CHANGE M/F AND PROCESS M/F ARE DIFFERENT
E-31 NEXT PROC THAT CHANGED K CHG DATE ISN'T CHANGED
E-32 BECAUSE IT ISN'T TUNNEL LOC, KANBAN KIND MUST INPUT
E-33 CHANGE DATE IS SMALLER THAN LOCATION M/F OPEN LOC DATE
E-34 KANBAN CHANGE DATE IS NOT INPUT
E-35 THOUGH IT IS TUNNEL PROCESS, KANBAN KIND IS INPUT
E-36 IMPOSSIBLE TO ADD PROC AT CHG SCREEN FOR RELATIVE C_P/N
E-37 IMPOSSIBLE TO CHG DATE AT CHG SCREEN FOR RELATIVE C_P/N
E-38 IT WAS CHANGED PROC, BUT KANBAN CHG DATE DOESN'T CHG
     LOC OF PROC ISN'T INPUT IN INTRA-PROC LOC M/F
     IT'S DIFFERENT FROM LOC M/F IN KANBAN KIND OF PROC
E-41 BACK THE VALUE BEFORE. PROC NO MUSTN'T CHG BEFORE ENTER
E-42 COMMON P/N IS + AT THIS PROC NO. NOT CHG TO TUNNEL LOC
E-43 NEXT PROC K CHG DATE OF THE PROC WHICH CHANGED IS SMALL
E-44 PROC NO THAT IT WAS APPOINTED INPUT BY A MINUS VALUE
E-45 INPUT CHANGE DATE BIGGER THAN 0
E-46 INPUT CHANGE DATE BY A DATE FROM
E-47 INPUT CHANGE DATE BY A DATE FROM TODAY
E-48 IN CASE OF INST KANBAN INPUT MCH NO OF QUENCHING PROC
E-49 BECAUSE IT IS QUENCHING PROCESS MATERIAL(999) CHANGE
E-50 H IS INPUT INTO THE THIRD COLUMN OF SURFACE TREATMENT
E-51 INPUT CHANGE DATE (SURFACE CHANGED)
